Event Check-in & Badging

Impress your guests with a hassle free Event Check-in experience.

Provide a no-queue, seamless experience through instant QR scanning & on-site printing of high-quality custom event badges.

Get started

Deliver the most engaging digital event experience

Integrated interactive experience that integrates digital content, live streaming, networking, and sponsorship options for maximum ROI

Self-Service Check-In

Enable your attendees to quickly check-in, grab their badge and enter your event venue in seconds.

On-Demand Badge Printing

Pre-print badges with event branding or on-demand during onsite QR check-in.

Offline Capabilities

Poor network at the venue? No worries, our offline mode will allow you to check in guests and print badges as usual.

Touchless event check-in

Simplify your check-in process through QR code scanning, seamlessly connected from your invitation emails.

  • Branded self check-in kiosk screen
  • Search and check in
  • Self registration for walk-ins
  • Badge auto-print upon check-in

Quickly search for the people you need to

Micepad’s intuitive interface provides you with a centralised contact list, allowing you to quickly searchthrough your guest list with ease.

On-demand Badge Printing

Printing badges with Micepad gives you the ability to print badges before the event, on event day, and manage name tags for walk-in and last-minute registrations.

  • Instant printing
  • Easily edit details and reprint badges
  • Wired and Wireless connections
  • Supports Inkjet, Thermal and Label printers

Flexible registration for last minute changes

Quickly and easily register any new guests with a highly customisable form on our provided iPads or on your own device, at any point throughout the event.

Frequently Asked Questions

What is a check-in app for events?

Check-in app for events is a digital solution for the attendee registration process. It also enables online or in-person participants to quickly and seamlessly check in for the event by scanning the QR code as well as provides a hassle-free experience.

What is contactless event registration?

Check-in app for events is a digital solution for the attendee registration process. It also enables online or in-person participants to quickly and seamlessly check in for the event by scanning the QR code as well as provides a hassle-free experience.

How do event organizers keep track of guest at the event?

Micepad check in apps for events provides a modern way to keep track of the attendees such as

  1. Self-Service Check-In: Allows attendees quickly check in by scanning the QR code and grabbing their badge as fast as possible.
  2. On-Demand Badge Printing: Pre-print badges with event branding or on-demand during onsite QR check-in
  3. Offline Capabilities: we will help you to check in guests and print badges
Can Micepads event check in app handle last-minute registration?

Yes, we can handle last-minute changes and we are flexible enough and make the registration process easy and quick for added new guests whether is walk-ins or last-minute registration.

How does the self registration kiosk work

We offer self-check-in registration kiosks where attendees can register without physical contact efficiently. Our user-friendly Kiosk also includes the features such as badge auto-print upon check-in and self-registration for walk-ins.

What's the advantage of offline capabilities in Micepad's check-in app?

Micepad’s check-in app offers offline capabilities, ensuring event check-in is uninterrupted even if the network connection is poor. You can still check in guests and print badges seamlessly.
